---
title: Quick Creamy Chicken Fusilli with Capsicum Relish & Tomato
description: Anything and everything can go into a fusilli pasta, but this one has something a little special. That rich red and creamy sauce comes
from the addition of chargrilled capsicum relish. It covers the chicken and spinach perfectly creating yet another amazing bowl of fusilli.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-fusilli-9284d757.jpg
